<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>喝酒 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E5%96%9D%E9%85%92/</link><description>Recent content in 喝酒 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 20 Mar 2011 08:24:56 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E5%96%9D%E9%85%92/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>喝酒那点事儿</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/drinking/</link><pubDate>Sun, 20 Mar 2011 08:24:56 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/drinking/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了作者对喝酒的态度和一些关于自己喝酒的经历。作者并不喜欢喝酒，但别人常觉得他喝酒厉害。作者只喝醉过两次，一次是被朋友给喝醉，另一次是在家里尝试蛇和青蛙的酒。作者怀念小时候的家乡和一起喝酒的快乐时光。尽管生活中对喝酒有些负面经历，但作者还是对童年时的酒感到向往。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/drinking/featured.png"/></item><item><title>朋友小聚</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/friends-gathering/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 Feb 2011 17:00:21 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/friends-gathering/</guid><description>朋友们从不同地方聚会，但时间晚了找不到吃饭的地方。最后他们在烧烤摊包下来吃饭，然后打牌、喝酒。作者困了就睡觉，和朋友开玩笑说小时候梦想成真了。第二天早上有人还在打牌，大家散去约好晚上再见面。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/friends-gathering/featured.png"/></item><item><title>昨天喝醉了... 貌似...</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/drunk-yesterday/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Oct 2008 11:50:04 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/drunk-yesterday/</guid><description>文章讲述了作者昨天喝醉后的一些模糊记忆，包括喝了几瓶啤酒和二锅头，感觉有点醉，但清醒后应该要回忆起来。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/drunk-yesterday/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>